---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import MagneticButton from '../../components/MagneticButton.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Afri Educare Alliance" description="Case study: Embedding ethics into storytelling from day one.">

  <section class="pt-32 pb-12 bg-warm-white">
    <div class="max-w-[800px] mx-auto px-6 md:px-16">
      <a href="/projects" class="text-[13px] text-text-soft no-underline hover:text-terracotta transition-colors mb-6 inline-block reveal">&larr; Back to Projects</a>
      <h1 class="font-serif text-[38px] lg:text-[48px] text-navy leading-[1.1] reveal">Afri Educare Alliance</h1>
      <p class="font-serif text-[20px] text-text-muted mt-3 reveal">Embedding ethics into storytelling from day one.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-6 bg-warm-white">
    <div class="max-w-[800px] mx-auto px-6 md:px-16">
      <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-6 text-[13px] text-text-soft border-y border-navy/[0.06] py-5 reveal">
        <div><span class="text-navy font-medium">Client:</span> Afri Educare Alliance</div>
        <div><span class="text-navy font-medium">Role:</span> Co-Founder, Board Member & Communications Lead</div>
        <div><span class="text-navy font-medium">Timeline:</span> Ongoing since 2016</div>
      </div>
      <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2 mt-4 reveal">
        <span class="text-[11px] px-3 py-1 rounded-full cat-ethical">Advocacy & Ethical Storytelling</span>
        <span class="text-[11px] px-3 py-1 rounded-full cat-community">Communication & PR Education</span>
        <span class="text-[11px] px-3 py-1 rounded-full cat-lifestyle">Personal Branding & Voice</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-16 bg-warm-white">
    <div class="max-w-[800px] mx-auto px-6 md:px-16 space-y-12">

      <div class="bg-cream rounded-lg p-6 border-l-3 border-amber reveal">
        <p class="text-[14px] text-navy leading-relaxed">
          <strong>A Note on This Partnership:</strong> My work with AECA originates from my foundational role as its Co-Founder. At Tama PR, we offer the same depth of strategic communications counsel and ethical storytelling services to our external clients.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="reveal">
        <h2 class="font-serif text-[24px] text-navy mb-4">Philosophy & Alignment</h2>
        <p class="text-[16px] leading-[1.8] text-text-muted">
          Afri Educare Alliance was founded on a belief that its work should one day no longer be necessary — that a more humane, equitable society would ensure every child has access to education, healthcare, and basic dignity without intervention. Tama PR's collaboration with AECA is grounded in this philosophy.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="reveal">
        <h2 class="font-serif text-[24px] text-navy mb-4">The Approach</h2>
        <ul class="space-y-4 text-[15px] text-text-muted">
          <li class="flex gap-3"><span class="text-terracotta mt-1">&#9679;</span> <span><strong class="text-navy">Advocacy & Ethical Storytelling:</strong> Established protocols to ensure every community narrative was shared with dignity, context, and consent.</span></li>
          <li class="flex gap-3"><span class="text-terracotta mt-1">&#9679;</span> <span><strong class="text-navy">Communication & PR Education:</strong> Built the team's internal capacity, training them to become clear, confident storytellers of their own work.</span></li>
          <li class="flex gap-3"><span class="text-terracotta mt-1">&#9679;</span> <span><strong class="text-navy">Personal Branding & Voice:</strong> Defined AECA's organizational voice to be as authentic and principled as its mission.</span></li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="reveal">
        <h2 class="font-serif text-[24px] text-navy mb-4">The Work</h2>
        <ul class="space-y-3 text-[15px] text-text-muted">
          <li class="flex gap-3"><span class="text-terracotta mt-1">&#9679;</span> Crafted the core messaging framework transforming complex social challenges into compelling, human-centered narratives</li>
          <li class="flex gap-3"><span class="text-terracotta mt-1">&#9679;</span> Guided ethical storytelling practices ensuring community members are active participants in their stories</li>
          <li class="flex gap-3"><span class="text-terracotta mt-1">&#9679;</span> Developed strategic communication plans bridging immediate impact reporting with long-term advocacy goals</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="reveal">
        <h2 class="font-serif text-[24px] text-navy mb-4">The Impact</h2>
        <div class="space-y-4 text-[15px] text-text-muted">
          <p><strong class="text-navy">For AECA:</strong> Achieved increased visibility and credibility within critical networks with a consistently clear, principled voice.</p>
          <p><strong class="text-navy">For the Mission:</strong> Elevated storytelling from a marketing tool to a core practice of empowerment.</p>
          <p><strong class="text-navy">For Tama PR:</strong> This project is the living embodiment of our ethos — communication rooted in deep philosophical alignment.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Testimonial -->
      <div class="bg-cream rounded-xl p-8 border-l-4 border-terracotta reveal">
        <p class="font-serif text-[20px] italic text-navy leading-relaxed mb-3">
          "Tama helped us understand that our story isn't something we tell — it's something we live."
        </p>
        <span class="text-[13px] text-terracotta font-medium">— Evans Odhiambo, Executive Director</span>
      </div>

      <div class="text-center pt-4 reveal">
        <p class="text-[16px] text-text-muted mb-6">You need communication that protects as much as it amplifies. Let's build that together.</p>
        <MagneticButton href="/contact" variant="primary">Let's Talk About Your Advocacy Work</MagneticButton>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

</BaseLayout>
